				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Quan-H%C3%A1n-Khanh/B%C3%ADch-ng%E1%BB%8Dc-ti%C3%AAu-k%E1%BB%B3-04/poem-GLzqIGvVnoBURna-hgD_jw">Bích ngọc tiêu kỳ 04 - 碧玉簫其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Quan-H%C3%A1n-Khanh/author-YR1JO8YsFFO7R_h7lgqsNQ">Quan Hán Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/C%E1%BB%ADu-v%C5%A9-k%E1%BB%B3-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-b%E1%BA%A5t-ch%C3%AD/poem-O0yUQ5SxwKoB3k65UN1KKQ">Cửu vũ kỳ Vương tướng quân bất chí - 久雨期王將軍不至</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-V%E1%BB%8B/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-T%E1%BB%91ng-nh%C3%A2n-ho%E1%BA%A1-thu%E1%BB%B5-khuy%E1%BB%83n/poem-AhhCcTGvVkO4nFsGdjjNMA">Đề Tống nhân hoạ thuỵ khuyển - 題宋人畫睡犬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-V%E1%BB%8B/author-cFaiJWajT_3vfsAWKg1raQ">Từ Vị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/L%E1%BB%AF-t%E1%BA%A5n-kh%E1%BB%91c-n%E1%BB%99i/poem-P2srIU4fe6hXa0pWW9JrBA">Lữ tấn khốc nội - 旅殯哭內</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/M%E1%BB%A5c-ng%C6%B0u-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-LnGO_skTPSV8gaambRvGVw">Mục ngưu từ - 牧牛詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-72N6ob4Hsg7Gc-KrAOsrTA">Viên Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%C3%A1t-s%C6%B0-l%C3%A3o/Ph%C3%B3ng-vi%C3%AAn/poem-kW-d44fYJ3cmjsaataQ2rQ">Phóng viên - 放猿</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%C3%A1t-s%C6%B0-l%C3%A3o/author-sclZV9StpgYyM9mllGil2Q">Cát sư lão</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Nh%E1%BA%A5t/T%E1%BA%ADt-t%C3%A0-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-nh%E1%BB%8B-L%E1%BB%97-sinh-ca/poem-oYHOX9QnZMy3kWU23QKbaQ">Tật tà thi kỳ nhị (Lỗ sinh ca) - 疾邪詩其二（魯生歌）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Nh%E1%BA%A5t/author--ppSF8KhTOlbANcnV7XUYg">Triệu Nhất</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/Thu-H%E1%BB%93-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-zDQoXCerAIEwqageOYXxZw">Thu Hồ hành kỳ 1 - 秋胡行其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/author-_plJ3nwj8cVN02KPZ4P_8g">Tào Phi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-6/poem-TsZkU2nkVdDsx-KdZYlTKA">Thường đệ 6 - 裳棣 6</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Y%E1%BA%BFn/poem-JKT7bPG0eROkAd3mZfKonA">Yến - 燕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-Kr7fkwn4MlJgFpxLge_BJw">Đằng Bạch</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
